name: Artistic Works of Bob Ross
content:
Description: statistical analysis of 403 episodes of Painting with Bob Ross, including details on elements he painted in each episode.

[Source](https://github.com/fivethirtyeight/data/tree/master/bob-ross)

Columns:

* EPISODE (string): Season and episode count for that given episode
* TITLE (string): Title of that given episode
* All other columns, such as BEACH, BUILDING, TREES (number): how many of that given painting element were painted by Bob Ross in the episode
